H. Sanford Riley's Biography




			Mr. Riley was appointed Chairman of North West in June, 2008. Mr. Riley has been President and CEO of Richardson Financial Group Limited since 2003. He held the positions of Chairman of Investors Group Inc. from 2001 to 2002, and President and CEO of Investors Group Inc. from 1992 to 2001. He is a former director of GMP Capital Inc. and Manitoba Telecom Services Inc. In addition to the public company directorships set out below, Mr. Riley is the Chairman of the University of Winnipeg Foundation. Mr. Riley was appointed to the Order of Canada in July, 2002.
		
Source: The North West Company Inc. on 04/05/2017
		
	

 






